name: CALGARY CITY VIEWS! Flair Airlines 737 MAX Midnight Takeoff from YYC
description:
Merry Christmas everyone! Thanks so much for all of your support over this past year :)

Here's a quick wing view video, taking off from runway 17L at Calgary International Airport on board this Flair Airlines 737 MAX, on a late night flight over to Vancouver!
